processProtocol.name: processProtocol
processProtocol.hint_desc: Either "Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: SelectedProtocolFromClientList\r\n" or return an empty string. The carriage return/newline combo must appear at the end of a non-empty string, and must not appear at the beginning of the string nor in an otherwise empty string, or it will be considered part of the response body, which will trigger an error in the client as it will not be formatted correctly.
